title: 4 Teasers Zed, Sona, Garen, Vi
body: Its been bugging me so much, but i'm not 100% sure, so can anyone tell me. Its the damn music track it has playing the same as the one they use in Fable II, like seriously it is so similar, but im not 100% sure and i want to know.

replies.body:
Ahaha it's just 2 notes a step down apart. 

It's so little information you can't even tell what key it's in, let alone if it's like any other song. Could be anything really.
